  <brief_title>Comparison of STOP-BANG and DES-OSA as Predictive Score for Difficult Intubation.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of STOP-BANG and DES-OSA as Predictive Score for Difficult Intubation Among Patients Scheduled for Bariatric Surgery.</official_title>
